{"tid":405673,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉：愛國不等如愚蠢說話　指「愚蠢愛國者」不利國家","createTime":"2017-09-19T04:42:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T18:15:07.000Z","uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e303482d411335636d6a2e092f725818d39e51b","tid":405673,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T04:42:10.000Z","msg":"立法會議員何君堯「殺無赦」論風波持續，行會成員、新民黨主席葉劉淑儀強調，「愛國」不等如以愚蠢方式說話或行動，「如何君堯（like Junius Ho）」。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀昨於facebook講述她在《明報》撰寫的＜遏止港獨硬不來＞文章，提到政府現階段應先處理迫切民生議題以維持民望，如為了校園「港獨」標語風波令社會再添紛亂，只會得不償失，實屬不智。<br />\n<br />\n有網民認為葉劉淑儀「講得太好了」，但亦有網民批評其言論「愈來愈不持平」，「奉勸葉劉，把不應該說的話，掛在口邊，才是實屬不智」。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀隨後以英文回應，強調「愛國不等如以愚蠢方式說話或行動，如何君堯（Loving our country does not mean acting or speaking in a stupid way, like Junius Ho）」。<br />\n<br />\n她又說，「愚蠢愛國者 （stupid &quot;patriots&quot;）」對國家沒有好處，「包括可能不少人被聘請成為『愛國者』（including possibly quite a few hired to become &quot;patriots&quot;）」。"},{"pid":"54e54adaf01cd51ec9017219a58164dd94dbe9ad","tid":405673,"uid":28151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T04:46:54.000Z","msg":"Patriotism is the last refuge of a scoundrel<br />\n08年仲有人同你講愛國，咁短時間咁多人講港獨真係自己拎嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769c11b15df8fd3943fa177ebd883cc0d7e21dfc","tid":405673,"uid":70028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T05:16:32.000Z","msg":"葉劉就死？講野咁持平既"},{"pid":"28ecf2d5ce56bc86742ffd5ecfb455183ee344b8","tid":405673,"uid":48679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T05:18:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>葉劉就死？講野咁持平既</blockquote><br />\n點都要有人扮中間派，吸班離地撚既票"},{"pid":"66bbca001337a13fc7e5da79660009fe90b010f7","tid":405673,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T05:22:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>葉劉就死？講野咁持平既</blockquote><br />\n點都要有人扮中間派，吸班離地撚既票</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有何鳩搖、鳩浩頂、糧尾分同割配煩呢班仆街<br />\n葉劉已經算比較唔克人憎"},{"pid":"9532b90e47c1bb2b39426c1c050103aa40e22a63","tid":405673,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T05:25:14.000Z","msg":"忽然坦白 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673eafb8d709cb4ffff14353aaef2f4b6e23e6e7","tid":405673,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T05:28:10.000Z","msg":"幫港獨講說話即係支持港獨，一樣要殺無赦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66812fb85e2e22e1a16201afa83681d9ee2e394c","tid":405673,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T05:29:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>葉劉就死？講野咁持平既</blockquote><br />\n點都要有人扮中間派，吸班離地撚既票</blockquote><br />\n大把人buy呢套"},{"pid":"6d7ac7c560e3ad3c4b9cee36d2bfb102bcd8a3e6","tid":405673,"uid":137627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T05:31:57.000Z","msg":"「包括可能不少人被聘請成為『愛國者』<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb3bce90432ce53b1244f3ddc4b91168519d7d3","tid":405673,"uid":38795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T18:15:07.000Z","msg":"當年佢咁辛苦推23條<br />\n而家想做特首結果俾主人違棄<br />\n連薯片都有得入閘，佢反而閘都入唔到<br />\n今日條氣緊係唔順啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}